Download

You can click link below to download

Download

Using on the web

You need to copy the entire UIIconFont directory into your project folder. In the <head> of your html, reference the location to your ui-icon/css/style.css.

Here’s an example:

<link rel="stylesheet" href="myProjects/webProject/ui-icon/css/style.css">

Example

< i class="uii-arrow-bottom-right-outline"> </i>
< i class=" uii-arrow-down-3-outline"> </i>
< i class="  uii-arrow-bottom-right-outline"> </i>
